item.title: TBB-10-High-Voltage-Collective-Compensation-Device
item.description: The TBB-10 high-voltage collective compensation device mainly avoids the disadvantages of large local compensation investment, equipment maintenance, and decentralized operation management. The centralized compensation device is mainly used in 3-10kV three-phase power frequency AC power system with small load changes.
